+# Cross-origin / DNS-rebinding gate (issue #228). Both servers reflect only
+# allowlisted Origins (never a wildcard) and reject non-allowlisted Host
+# headers. Loopback (127.0.0.1 / localhost / [::1]) for each bound port is
